{"tid":1822113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪70歲老伯過馬路 遭綠Van撞斃","createTime":"2020-01-12T17:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T18:51:51.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c19ea7d0fd53f352482e1805e802a2d93ecda8f3","tid":1822113,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200112/large/1578835058_1ee1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578835058_1ee1.jpg&h=f575e7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【23:55】警方表示，54歲小巴司機涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人死亡被捕，現正被扣留調查，東九龍總區交通部特別調查隊正跟進調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚6時許，一輛往淘大花園的89A專線小巴，駛經秀茂坪安秀道，近安泰邨錦泰樓對出時位置時，突然有一名70歲男子橫過馬路，小巴收掣不及撞倒男子，小巴司機見狀隨即報警。<br />\n<br />\n意外後涉事小巴車頭凹陷，擋風玻璃破裂；而傷者則被小巴撞飛約5米，墮地重創。救護員到場後，隨即將傷者送聯合醫院搶救，惜終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，安秀道往寶達邨方向近安泰邨的全線現已封閉。部份巴士路線須改道行駛。"},{"pid":"11ba93888450f8e17b1f3d4802d359e134b6759c","tid":1822113,"uid":233643,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"一石二鳥<br />\n撚手無兩件廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2183bb40d89c9e5e29862ba01f9a99d81a1cf786","tid":1822113,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:41:06.000Z","msg":"又小巴佬"},{"pid":"b7a252f7d5423bf89eee619265bb3c1267d56438","tid":1822113,"uid":15159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"諗起張gif"},{"pid":"12e28b1a92127dbb88947925b8daf10d8603fdc4","tid":1822113,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"呢d人收錢架"},{"pid":"27a2f4e47a4e0ca4088770cd3b758559ba241212","tid":1822113,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害死個司機"},{"pid":"42bbdb733d8b5a8299a07b2671450e751b02830